data.name: Silverdale
data.description: The front entrance is covered by a wide porch lined with double columns. Inside, the foyer leads past the formal dining room and the den/bed 5 that is accessed through double doors. Just beyond the foyer are wide-open views to the covered lanai through the great room and kitchen areas. The great room is topped with a stunning 2-story ceiling. A fireplace is centered between built-ins. French doors open to the deep covered lanai with outdoor kitchen. The secluded owner’s suite has its own private entrance just off the great room and has outdoor access. The spacious bedroom has views to the rear. A short hallway leads past the walk-in-shower, double sink vanity, free-standing tub, private privy and ends at the large walk-in-closet. A guest bedroom with full bath is located across the home. Its full bath can easily double as a cabana bath for a pool home. Upstairs, a bridge overlooks the great room. Two bedrooms share a full bath which can also be accessed from the media room.

data.name: Burien
data.description: Lots of transom windows bring extra light into this splendid Contemporary house plan. On the main floor, the open living area of the combined kitchen, dining room and living room - open to above - gives a spacious feeling. The kitchen island has two sinks, a dishwasher, prep space and provides seating for three people. Back to back fireplaces warm the great room and the front patio. The master bedroom has access to the outside, a five fixture bath and a walk-in closet. Upstairs, the front room overlooks the living room below and can be used as a bedroom or loft. A bedroom and bath complete the floor.

data.name: Pacific Heights
data.description: Stone accents and glass garage doors embellish the front of this smartly designed, 2-story modern house plan. Just inside from the shelter of the covered front porch, guests are welcomed by expansive views of the family room and naturally illuminated dining area beyond. The dining area lies open to the kitchen which features an island with a breakfast bar, ample counter space, and roomy walk-in pantry. Upstairs, the master suite well separated from the secondary bedrooms. This master suite features a walk-in closet and a bath with dual sinks, soaking tub and shower. Bedrooms 3 and 4 each have walk-in closets and share a jack and jill bath.  Bedroom 2 has its own bathroom and a walk-in closet. The upstairs laundry room includes a folding counter, soaking sink, and nearby linen closet is convenient to all of the bedrooms.

data.name: Margate
data.description: Classic Mediterranean stylings, mixed with some modern accent pieces give this house a unique facade. A grand entry greets guests with its double-sided fireplace that is shared with the great room. Just off the entry to the right, you'll find a stunning den that brings in a ton of natural light with its large windows. Much like the den, the great room also lets in a ton of light with 6 sets of french doors. The kitchen features a large island with a prep sink and a walk-in pantry.  Also on the main floor for ultimate convenience, the master suite includes a soaking tub, enclosed toilet, his/her vanities, and an amazing walk-in shower that is accessible from the outside to make it easier to wash up after using your hot tub in the amazing courtyard. Upstairs, you will find 3 additional bedrooms and a wonderful family room. A study with a built-in desk is a perfect place to get work done. Bedroom 4 shares a bathroom with the family room while bedroom 2 and 3 share a bathroom. A deck is accessible from the family room.

data.name: Fairwood Place
data.description: This spacious contemporary prairie home has lots of living space. Work from home in your quiet front-facing den or spend time in the huge, informal area in back, where the open layout unites the dining room, kitchen and great room. Flex space can be whatever you need and views of the outdoor living can be seen from three rooms. All four bedrooms are on the upper floor with two bathrooms to serve the secondary bedrooms. The master suite has its own private bathroom and a large walk-in closet.

data.name: Highland Park
data.description: If you've been challenged with the task of building on a narrow strip of property, Highland Park is perfect for you. Whether you are building on an infill lot or trying to replace an older house in an urban environment, this plan accommodates even the narrowest of lots. The Highland Park comes in at an efficient 20' wide. Even though the house is narrow, it doesn't sacrifice any amenities. Inside the home, the great room, dining room, and kitchen flow perfectly in an open layout. The kitchen includes an island and a walk-in pantry. The great room is warmed by a fireplace and allows plenty of natural light through its windows. The master bedroom includes his/her vanities and a soaking tub. Bedrooms 2 and 3 share a centrally located bathroom.

data.name: Turtle Run
data.description: This cozy beach home is focused on outdoor living. With a front covered screen porch, upper sun deck, entertaining balcony complete with bar, and viewing tower you will not miss a view. The open main floor with family, dining, and kitchen flow great for entertaining. A large foyer and mud room off the side entry and garage provide ample storage. The second floor stair hall has access to the sun deck, as does the private master suite. An additional guest suite and family living or game room occupy this floor. The third floor provides another guest suite as well as bunk rooms for the kids. An entertaining balcony with bar and viewing tower is the perfect spot for a drink and sunset gathering.

data.name: Mirrormont
data.description: The design is efficient and the footprint is square which helps control building costs. The living spaces flow together at the rear of the home and are replete with amenities. The kitchen includes an island counter, the dining room offers a built-in hutch and French doors, and the great room provides a fireplace and built-in cabinets. An office, powder room, and laundry room are clustered together at the front of the main level. The upper level contains three bedrooms placed at separate ends of the staircase landing and hallway for privacy. The master suite includes a wall of windows with transoms, a walk-in closet, and a private bath with large shower. The secondary bedrooms share a bath that has separate compartments for the sink and the tub and toilet.

data.name: Smithson

The kitchen features a massive, multi-purpose island and a pantry sits within arms reach for convenience. Retreat to the main-level, master suite for peace and quiet, and discover an attached bath with a separate tub and walk-in shower. Floating stairs serve as a focal point in the great room, and lead to the second level, which consists of a home office and a second bedroom with a full bath. Each room upstairs includes a private balcony. The exterior of the detached garage matches that of the main home, and offers four garage bays for vehicles or all-terrain toys.

The master bathroom includes a wetroom, an enclosed toilet, double vanities, a makeup counter, and a large walk-in closet. The master bedroom also has access to the front patio. On the second floor, you'll find 3 additional bedrooms. Bedroom 2 has access to its own bathroom while bedrooms 2 and 3 share a jack and jill bathroom. Each bedroom enjoys its own walk-in closet. A large loft area with a built-in entertainment center makes for a great playroom for the kids.

There is a loft space on the second floor that makes for a perfect playroom.

data.name: Manorwood
data.description: The elegant exterior of this European home is set off by a gorgeous round window on the second floor. Wide arched entryways add a custom touch and enhance the views between rooms. The optional screened porch is delightful for eating outdoors. The first floor guest suite has a private bathroom and is ideal for family members who are visiting. Built-ins and a walk-in storage closet make the home office more functional. Homeowners gets a lovely master suite and a spacious master bathroom with giant walk-in closet. On the upper floor, two built-in desks help keep the kids organized.

data.name: Poplar View
data.description: A beautiful contrast of board and batten siding on the exterior gives the Poplar View a beautiful Modern Farmhouse curb appeal. This stunning home includes a ton of outdoor space including a front covered porch, 2 rear covered patios, an outdoor kitchen, and 2 decks on the upper level. The massive great room is warmed by a fireplace that is flanked by built-in bookshelves and is well lit with natural light from the beautiful door that leads to the covered patio. This homes amazing kitchen includes a large island and a large walk-in pantry. A door on the rear of the kitchen leads to an outdoor kitchen with a cooktop. Upstairs, you will find a stunning master bedroom that includes a wetroom with a soaking tub and shower, his/her vanities, and a large walk-in closet with access to the laundry room. A large sliding door leads from the master bedroom to a private deck. A loft area on the second floor also has a sliding door that leads to a deck.

data.name: Coronado
data.description: The Coronado plan is a stunning Modern style home that showcases single pitched rooflines and cedar accents. An entry with a 2 story ceiling greets you as soon as you step in the front door. Further, into the home, the dining room, great room, and kitchen all flow perfectly together. The kitchen includes a large island with a snack bar and a large walk-in pantry. The great room is warmed by a fireplace that is flanked by built-in bookshelves and accesses the rear of the home through a triple sliding glass door. Upstairs, you'll find all 4 bedrooms. The master suite includes his/her vanities, a walk-in closet, a soaking tub, and an enclosed toilet area. Bedroom 2 has access to its own bathroom while bedroom 3 and 4 share a convenient bathroom.
